8
00:03:18,965 --> 00:03:21,843
Idemo, Kide.
Hajde, Dok.

9
00:03:23,177 --> 00:03:26,097
Hodaj. Hodaj. Smireno.

10
00:03:34,522 --> 00:03:38,067
Hajde, Kide!
- Samo trenutak, Ded.

11
00:03:38,151 --> 00:03:40,361
Ova mlada dama
pokušava da me obmane.

12
00:03:43,823 --> 00:03:45,617
