Brže!
Uzmi zlato! Uzmi zlato!

77
00:11:57,650 --> 00:12:00,027
Požuri.
Hajde. Hajde.

78
00:12:18,838 --> 00:12:20,548
Požurite!

79
00:12:22,633 --> 00:12:25,928
