80
00:12:26,804 --> 00:12:29,765
<i>Prekinite s paljbom!
U zaklon!</i>

81
00:12:29,849 --> 00:12:32,768
<i>Hajde, idemo! Idemo!</i>

82
00:12:52,788 --> 00:12:54,707
