103
00:14:21,085 --> 00:14:22,711
U redu.

104
00:14:32,221 --> 00:14:33,722
Ti jašeš.

105
00:14:43,399 --> 00:14:45,901
Bolje da brišeš odavde.

106
00:14:49,989 --> 00:14:51,740
Brzo se vraćam.

107
00:15:01,125 --> 00:15:03,252
Kide. - Da?

108
