115
00:16:23,666 --> 00:16:27,544
<i>Kako ste? - Dobro.</i>

116
00:16:27,628 --> 00:16:30,089
Koliko za ona dva konja?

117
00:16:33,384 --> 00:16:35,386
<i>Kako mogu da vam pomognem?</i>

118
00:16:36,428 --> 00:16:38,263
<i>Koliko za ona dva konja?</i>

119
00:16:39,264 --> 00:16:42,184
<i>Nisu na prodaju</i>

120
00:16:42,267 --> 00:16:44,019
