121
00:16:46,146 --> 00:16:48,899
<i>Prekini. Koliko?</i>

122
00:16:50,109 --> 00:16:52,111
<i>Koliko? - Dvesta pezosa.</i>

123
00:16:53,112 --> 00:16:56,615
<i>Dvesta pezosa.
- Idi, Manuele.</i>

124
00:16:58,283 --> 00:16:59,868
Brže!

125
00:17:35,571 --> 00:17:36,697
<i>Dodaj mi torbu.</i>

126
00:18:52,105 --> 00:18:53,941
<i>Hvala, stari.</i>

127
00:20:01,842 --> 00:20:05,596
<i>Horhe! Karlose!
Idite i uhvatite ga!</i>

128
00:20:19,651 --> 00:20:21,778
<i>Stoj!</i>

129
00:20:21,862 --> 00:20:23,697
<i>Ostanite na okupu!</i>

130
00:20:27,034 --> 00:20:31,580
<i>Starče, da nisi video nekog gringa
kako prolazi ovuda u žurbi?</i>

131
00:20:31,663 --> 00:20:34,458
