166
00:24:35,031 --> 00:24:36,992
<i>Gde si bio?</i>

167
00:24:37,075 --> 00:24:39,411
<i>Svugde. - Dalje.</i>

168
00:24:39,494 --> 00:24:42,581
<i>Reci mi.
